### get tables by db id
GET http://{{baseURL}}/api/v1/metadata/table/db/4
Accept: application/json

### get table statistics by db id and table name
GET http://{{baseURL}}/api/v1/metadata/table/statistic/db-table
Accept: application/json

{"db_id": 4,"table_name": "test"}

### get table statistics by host info and db name and table name
GET http://{{baseURL}}/api/v1/metadata/table/statistic/host-info-db-table
Accept: application/json

{"host_ip": "127.0.0.1", "port_num": 3306, "db_name":"das", "table_name":"t_meta_mysql_cluster_info"}

### analyze table by db id and table name
POST http://{{baseURL}}/api/v1/metadata/table/analyze/db
Content-Type: application/json

{"db_id": 4,"table_name": "test", "account_name": "yc_guest"}

### analyze table by host info and db name and table name
POST http://{{baseURL}}/api/v1/metadata/table/analyze/host-info
Content-Type: application/json

{"host_ip": "127.0.0.1", "port_num": 3306, "db_name":"yc", "table_name":"test", "account_name": "yc_admin"}